name: Disabled Items Report
query:
SELECT
`tabFreezing Request`.`company` as "Company::200",
`tabFreezing Request`.`country` as "Country::80",
`tabFreezing Request`.`item` as "Item Code:Link/Item:100",
`tabFreezing Request`.`item_name` as "Item Name::250",
`tabFreezing Request`.`item_group` as "Item Group::100",
`tabItem Default`.default_warehouse as "Warehouse::150",
`tabItem Supplier`.supplier as "Supplier::150",
`tabItem Supplier`.supplier_part_no as "Part No::150",
`tabFreezing Request`.`creation` as "Posting Date:Date:100",
`tabFreezing Request`.`raised_by` as "Requested by::150",
`tabFreezing Request`.`workflow_state` as "Approval Status::150",
`tabFreezing Request`.`item_status` as "Item Status::120"
FROM
`tabFreezing Request`
Left Join `tabItem` ON `tabItem`.name =`tabFreezing Request`.item
Left Join `tabItem Default` ON `tabItem`.name =`tabItem Default`.parent
Left Join `tabItem Supplier` ON `tabItem`.name =`tabItem Supplier`.parent
